The '''''Krakana Current''''' was the personal starship of [[Quarren/Legends|Quarren]] [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Tikkes/Legends|Tikkes]], presumably a [[Mon Calamari Shipyards/Legends|Mon Calamari model]], during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was named after the fearsome [[Krakana/Legends|krakana]], a large, dangerous, carnivorous fish from Tikkes' homeworld of [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]].

==Behind the scenes==
This may be the name of Tikkes's [[Mon Calamari ceremonial ship]].

